{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/git/git-오류-해결방법/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Dryad","author":"dryad","siteUrl":"https://dryadsoft.github.io","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"dryadsoft/dryadsoft.github.io"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":"jbee"}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"aa02369f-9633-5a2e-8577-f63ba7c5707b","excerpt":"오류 발생 상황 ( package.json의 yarn deploy 실행 ) 발생오류 => A branch named ‘gh-pages’ already exists. 원인 Gthub의 기존 repositoroy를 삭제 및 생성을 몇번하면서 프로젝트의 branch cache가 남아있어서 발생한 문제 해결방법","html":"<h3 id=\"오류-발생-상황--packagejson의-yarn-deploy-실행-\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%98%A4%EB%A5%98-%EB%B0%9C%EC%83%9D-%EC%83%81%ED%99%A9--packagejson%EC%9D%98-yarn-deploy-%EC%8B%A4%ED%96%89-\" aria-label=\"오류 발생 상황  packagejson의 yarn deploy 실행  permalink\" class=\"anchor before\">true</a>오류 발생 상황 ( package.json의 yarn deploy 실행 )</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\">package.json\n<span class=\"token property\">\"scripts\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    ...\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"predeploy\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"yarn build\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"deploy\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"gh-pages -d build\"</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token function\">yarn</span> deploy</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"발생오류--a-branch-named-gh-pages-already-exists\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%B0%9C%EC%83%9D%EC%98%A4%EB%A5%98--a-branch-named-gh-pages-already-exists\" aria-label=\"발생오류  a branch named gh pages already exists permalink\" class=\"anchor before\">true</a>발생오류 => A branch named ‘gh-pages’ already exists.</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shellwrap\"><pre class=\"language-shellwrap\"><code class=\"language-shellwrap\">ProcessError: fatal: A branch named &#39;gh-pages&#39; already exists.\n\n    at ChildProcess.&lt;anonymous&gt; (D:\\workspace\\reactJs\\minsblog\\node_modules\\gh-pages\\lib\\git.js:42:16)\n    at ChildProcess.emit (events.js:210:5)\n    at maybeClose (internal/child_process.js:1021:16)\n    at Process.ChildProcess._handle.onexit (internal/child_process.js:283:5) {\n  code: 128,\n  message: &quot;fatal: A branch named &#39;gh-pages&#39; already exists.\\n&quot;,\n  name: &#39;ProcessError&#39;\n}</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"원인\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9B%90%EC%9D%B8\" aria-label=\"원인 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\">true</a>원인</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Gthub의 기존 repositoroy를 삭제 및 생성을 몇번하면서 프로젝트의 branch cache가 남아있어서 발생한 문제</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"해결방법\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%95%B4%EA%B2%B0%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95\" aria-label=\"해결방법 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\">true</a>해결방법</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token function\">rm</span> -rf node_modules/gh-pages/.cache</code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"git 오류 해결방법","date":"November 04, 2020"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/git/git-오류-해결방법/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/git/github-멀티계정-변경하기---ssh-key/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"github 멀티계정 변경하기 - ssh key","category":"git","draft":false}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/gulp.js/gulp---uglify를-이용하여-babel로-컴파일된-javascript-파일-축소하기/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"gulp - uglify를 이용하여 babel로 컴파일된 javascript 파일 축소하기","category":"gulp.js","draft":false}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3128451518","521680639"]}